# NOV DCS Support Assistant v2.0

> Enterprise Engineering Copilot for NOV Digital Control Systems

---

## Overview

NOV DCS Support Assistant v2.0 is an evidence-driven engineering assistant designed to support troubleshooting, documentation, diagnostics, training, and customer support across NOV Digital Control Systems.

Unlike traditional AI assistants, v2.0 follows structured engineering workflows instead of conversational reasoning.

Its purpose is to reduce troubleshooting time, improve documentation quality, standardize support practices, and capture engineering knowledge.

---

## Design Goals

- Evidence First
- Documentation Driven
- Engineering Consistency
- Root Cause Analysis
- Continuous Improvement
- Enterprise Ready

---

## Supported Products

- OrionNET
- Orion DAS
- Cerberus
- Argus TubeSpec
- CT-DOG
- ESS
- Remote Service Monitoring (RSM)
- Max Completions

